# Day 06 - Reverse & Aligned Patterns

## Problems Solved

### 1. Decreasing Number Pattern
1 2 3 4  
1 2 3  
1 2  
1  

- Logic:
  - Starting value is constant (1)
  - Number of elements decreases each row

